edit (distrib_areas_lines.txt):
    REPLACE WP    1    0    1     0     0    1    1
    BY      wrong 1    0    1     0     0    1    1
failure (2):: EOE
    Error: area 'wrong' not found in configuration file.
    (line 2 column 1 in 'distrib_areas_lines.txt')
EOE

